    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The body has noticeable rust, particularly around the wheel wells and undercarriage, and the paint is heavily faded with several dents. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a serious oil leak and the transmission shifts roughly; the interior also shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is best suited as a restoration project or a parts donor.",
