    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior still has that new-car feel with premium materials that show zero wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a whisper-quiet engine and incredibly smooth performance that must be experienced to be appreciated. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a showroom-quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag.",
      "price": 48500.0,
