      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$3,800 - Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration fans! This vehicle is the perfect project for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to its former glory. While it needs major mechanical and cosmetic work, it offers a fantastic foundation and an affordable start for your next big build!",
      "price": 3800.0,
