    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit exhibits a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom state, reflecting a history of meticulous care and uncompromising maintenance. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new assembly. For the discerning buyer seeking a specimen of peerless quality, this offering represents a rare acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning, flawless condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve completely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and professionally detailed. You won't find a single scratch or door ding anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to enjoy it. I'm happy to chat or answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically pristine, with the subframe integrity verified and rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance to factory specifications. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates, transferring power to the rear wheels via the variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing original-spec Sachs damping and fresh bushings for factory-new lateral grip. Finished in its original paint with zero discernible imperfections, the cabin retains its factory matte leather finish and functional switchgear. This is an unmodified, investment-grade example maintained to the highest mechanical standards.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. No accidents. Full service records. Non-smoker. Inspection ready.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a showroom. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, while the interior still carries that new-car scent. Every leather surface is supple and free of creases, and the dashboard is pristine without a hint of UV wear. Mechanically, it is flawless; I have a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed exclusively at the dealership. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. Includes all original manuals, two keys, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously curated vehicle, preserved in truly immaculate condition. This specimen represents the zenith of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom character. Every mechanical and aesthetic component has been subjected to rigorous scrutiny to ensure it adheres to the most exacting standards of excellence. For the discerning professional who demands uncompromising quality and an unparalleled driving experience, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
